# You are about breaking a centOS7 root passwd 

2-Eddit the kernel by adding
rd.break

3-Remount the sysroot directory to read and write.
mount -o remount,rw /sysroot 

4- Change the root directory to sysroot
chroot /sysroot

5-Administer new root password
passwd root (expl:abc123)

6-Relable the /etc/shadow file
touch /.autorelabel

7-exit 2x